This is the website for lilypond.org:

Required:

  * python
  * make
  
MAKING IT:

Type
	make

this will leave the site in the directory out/site/


DISTRIBUTION

* The format-page.py script is GPL

* Verbatim redistribution of the .html files and images is allowed and
  encouraged.

NOTE:

Links to the documentation must be site-absolute, eg

    href="/doc/v2.1/Documentation/out-www"

until someone fixes this.  The documentation is also on lilypond.org,
but not part of the website proper.  It is built from the lilypond
source package by running `make web'.


